# Post-change rebuild hints

Close with **Run the following:** and the relevant targets (omit when N/A). Full list: `make help`.

| If you changed… | Rebuild |
|-----------------|---------|
| `cmd/claudia`, most `internal/` (not indexer-only below) | `claudia-build` |
| Desktop / webview / CGO (`webview_*.go`, `default_mode_*.go`, `-tags desktop`) | `desktop-build` |
| `cmd/claudia-index`, `internal/indexer/` | `indexer-build` |

If the change needs a **fresh BiFrost / Qdrant / gateway metrics state**, also say: **`make clean-data CONFIRM=1`**.

Keep this short; do not paste Makefile excerpts into chat.
